    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't think there's an epilogue for me. i just feel like i've reached the end of the line. when you're at the last station and the train isn't going anywhere else, you don't look for a new direction... you just get off. it feels like the only logical thing to do is to just step off the tracks and let it be over.",
