      "content": "It is completely understandable that feeling stuck at the end of a journey can make letting go feel like the only logical choice. Sometimes, the bravest thing we can do is not force new chapters when the current one has truly run its course. Stepping away from the tracks isn't an ending, but rather a necessary rest before you can rebuild a path that fits who you are now.",
